<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 09:11:36 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>童话般的冰雕吸引大批游客来到中国哈尔滨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/fairy-tale-ice-sculptures-lure-droves-tourists-into-chinas-harbin-2024-01-05/</link><description>中国一年一度的冰雪节上周五开幕，童话般的冰雕吸引了大批游客，他们小心翼翼地在光滑的冰雪上拖行，拖着孩子乘坐雪橇在公园里转悠。</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 08:14:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/fairy-tale-ice-sculptures-lure-droves-tourists-into-chinas-harbin-2024-01-05/</guid></item><item><title>监管机构称特斯拉将在中国维修 162 万辆汽车</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-fix-162-mln-vehicles-china-regulator-2024-01-05/</link><description>市场监管机构周五表示，特斯拉正在中国有效召回 162 万辆汽车，包括其 S、X、3 和 Y 车型。</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 07:57:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-fix-162-mln-vehicles-china-regulator-2024-01-05/</guid></item><item><title>富士康预计第四季度需求放缓后第一季度收入下降</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/foxconn-december-sales-fall-269-year-earlier-2024-01-05/</link><description>全球最大的电子产品代工制造商和苹果最大的 iPhone 组装商台湾富士康周五表示，由于上一季度市场需求放缓，预计第一季度收入将在高基数基础上同比下降。</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 07:45:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/foxconn-december-sales-fall-269-year-earlier-2024-01-05/</guid></item><item><title>赛默飞停止在西藏销售法医技术</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/thermo-fisher-halts-forensic-tech-sales-tibet-2024-01-05/</link><description>赛默飞世尔科技发言人表示，该公司已承诺停止在西藏销售可用于识别个人身份的法医技术和设备。</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 07:37:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/thermo-fisher-halts-forensic-tech-sales-tibet-2024-01-05/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾国家安全顾问对中国外交保持开放态度</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-remains-open-diplomatic-discussions-with-china-national-security-2024-01-05/</link><description>菲律宾国家安全顾问周五在一份声明中表示，菲律宾仍然对与中国进行外交讨论持开放态度，并相信两国可以通过和平对话解决南海争端。</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 06:47:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-remains-open-diplomatic-discussions-with-china-national-security-2024-01-05/</guid></item><item><title>独家：中国推动股票基金推出以支持股市 - 消息人士</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-pushes-equity-fund-launches-support-stock-market-sources-2024-01-05/</link><description>四位直接了解此事的消息人士称，随着当局忙于重振落后的股市，北京已非正式地要求中国的一些基金管理公司优先推出股票基金，而不是债券基金等其他产品。</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 06:23:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-pushes-equity-fund-launches-support-stock-market-sources-2024-01-05/</guid></item><item><title>2024 年初台湾选举对美国稳定与中国关系的目标构成考验</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-election-poses-early-2024-test-us-aim-steady-china-ties-2024-01-05/</link><description>台湾下周的选举无论谁获胜都会给华盛顿带来挑战，执政党的胜利肯定会加剧与中国的紧张关系，而反对派的胜利可能会引发有关台湾国防政策的尴尬问题。</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 05:05:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-election-poses-early-2024-test-us-aim-steady-china-ties-2024-01-05/</guid></item><item><title>特斯拉凭借实时策略在中国销售效率超越比亚迪</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-trumps-byd-china-sales-efficiency-with-real-time-strategy-2024-01-05/</link><description>据三名知情人士透露，特斯拉在中国的战略是对销售人员进行实时、积极的管理，这使其门店比在全球最大汽车市场上销售比亚迪和其他品牌的经销商更具优势。</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 04:20:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-trumps-byd-china-sales-efficiency-with-real-time-strategy-2024-01-05/</guid></item><item><title>议员要求五角大楼考虑禁止美国投资中国移远通信</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/lawmakers-ask-pentagon-consider-barring-us-investments-chinas-quectel-2024-01-04/</link><description>美国众议院中国委员会的共和党和民主党最高领导人周四要求拜登政府考虑将中国移远无线公司列入中国军工企业名单。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 15:14:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/lawmakers-ask-pentagon-consider-barring-us-investments-chinas-quectel-2024-01-04/</guid></item><item><title>香港大亨律师就证人酷刑指控向联合国提出上诉</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kong-tycoons-lawyers-appeal-un-over-witness-torture-accusation-2024-01-04/</link><description>香港民主大亨黎智英的律师周四表示，他们已就一名证人在提供定罪证据之前受到酷刑的待遇问题向联合国酷刑问题专家提出上诉。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 14:40:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kong-tycoons-lawyers-appeal-un-over-witness-torture-accusation-2024-01-04/</guid></item><item><title>尽管与一家智能手机制造商达成协议，诺基亚在中国的专利纠纷仍然存在</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/media-telecom/nokias-patent-dispute-persists-china-despite-deal-with-one-smartphone-maker-2024-01-04/</link><description>芬兰电信设备制造商诺基亚周四表示，已与中国领先的智能手机制造商之一荣耀签署了 5G 专利协议，但其与其他中国公司的专利法律纠纷仍在继续。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 14:12:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/media-telecom/nokias-patent-dispute-persists-china-despite-deal-with-one-smartphone-maker-2024-01-04/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾军方：两艘中国船只尾随菲律宾和美国船只</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/two-chinese-vessels-shadowed-philippine-us-ships-philippine-military-2024-01-04/</link><description>菲律宾军方周四表示，两艘中国海军舰艇跟踪在南海进行联合巡逻的菲律宾和美国船只，因为该地区因领土主张争议而紧张局势加剧。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 14:03:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/two-chinese-vessels-shadowed-philippine-us-ships-philippine-military-2024-01-04/</guid></item><item><title>经过一年的事故和灾害，中国将解决安全风险</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-tackle-safety-risks-after-year-accidents-disasters-2024-01-04/</link><description>中国周四表示，计划开展为期三年的行动，以解决灾害和事故中影响反应速度的问题，包括采矿等行业的生产安全失误。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 13:12:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-tackle-safety-risks-after-year-accidents-disasters-2024-01-04/</guid></item><item><title>中国“冰城”哈尔滨元旦假期游客量创历史新高</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-ice-city-harbin-draws-record-tourists-over-new-year-holiday-2024-01-04/</link><description>中国东北黑龙江省的冰雪之都哈尔滨的“冰城”在新年假期吸引了创纪录的游客数量，其中许多人被一年一度的冰雪节宏伟而复杂的冰雕所吸引。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 10:06:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-ice-city-harbin-draws-record-tourists-over-new-year-holiday-2024-01-04/</guid></item><item><title>中国习近平就“恐怖袭击”向伊朗总统表示慰问</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/chinas-xi-sends-condolences-iran-president-terrorist-attack-2024-01-04/</link><description>中国国家电视台中央电视台称，中国国家主席习近平周四就一天前发生的“恐怖袭击”向伊朗总统致唁电。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 09:56:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/chinas-xi-sends-condolences-iran-president-terrorist-attack-2024-01-04/</guid></item></channel></rss>